def evaluateAlgorithm(X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test):
    
    # ------------------------------------------------------------------
    ## Compare different ML Algorithms with default parameter setting   
    # ------------------------------------------------------------------    
    model_List = []
    
    model_List.append(('LR',   'Logistic Regression ', LogisticRegression(random_state=0)))
    model_List.append(('SVC',   'Support Vector Machine ', SVC(probability=True,random_state=0)))
    model_List.append(('RF',   'Random Forest',       RandomForestClassifier(random_state=0)))
    model_List.append(('GB',   'Gradient Boosting Classifier ',  GradientBoostingClassifier(random_state=0))) 
   
 
    
    
     
    
    # ----------------------
    ## Cross Validation
    # ----------------------    
    print("Cross Validation Results ")
    outcomes = []
    description = []
    shortDescription = []
    for shtDes, des, model in model_List:
        cv_results = cross_val_score(model, X_train, y_train, cv = 10,
                                     scoring='accuracy', n_jobs = -1, verbose = 0)
        outcomes.append(cv_results)
        description.append(des)
        shortDescription.append(shtDes)
        prt_string = "\n %s:\n \tMean Accuracy: %f (Std: %f)" % (des,cv_results.mean()
                                                                    , cv_results.std())
        print(prt_string)

    # ------------------------------------------------------------------
    ## Visualise the outcomes / results from Cross Validation
    # ------------------------------------------------------------------    
    fig = plt.figure()
    fig.suptitle('Cross Validation Results (Algorithm Comparison)')
    plt.ylabel("Accuracy")
    plt.xlabel("Algorithm")
    ax = fig.add_subplot(111)
    plt.boxplot(outcomes)
    ax.set_xticklabels(shortDescription)
    plt.show()

    # ------------------------------------------------------------------    
    ## Training & Fitting of each Algorithm with training Dataset
    # ------------------------------------------------------------------    
    print('\nEvaluate Algorithms (Accuracy, Classification Report, Confusion Matrix) ... ... ... ')
    
    for shtDes, des, model in model_List:   
        
        #model fitting or training
        trained_Model = model.fit(X_train, y_train)
        
        ##Evaluation of trained Algorithm (or Model) and result
        pred_Class          = trained_Model.predict(X_test)
        acc         = accuracy_score(y_test, pred_Class)
        classReport = classification_report(y_test, pred_Class)
        confMatrix  = confusion_matrix(y_test, pred_Class) 

        print("\n%s: " % (des))
        print('The accuracy: {}'.format(acc))
        print('The Classification Report:\n {}'.format(classReport))
        print('The Confusion Matrix:\n {}'.format(confMatrix))

def evaluateAlgorithm2(X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test):
    
    # ------------------------------------------------------------------
    ## Compare different ML Algorithms with default parameter setting   
    # ------------------------------------------------------------------    
    model_List = []
    
    model_List.append(('LR',   'Logistic Regression ', LogisticRegression(**best_param_lr,random_state=0)))
    model_List.append(('SVC',   'Support Vector Machine ', SVC(**best_param_svm,random_state=0)))
    model_List.append(('RF',   'Random Forest',       RandomForestClassifier(**best_param_rf,random_state=0)))
    model_List.append(('GB',    'Gradient Boosting Classifier', GradientBoostingClassifier(**best_param_gb,random_state=0)))   
  
    
    
     
    
    # ----------------------
    ## Cross Validation
    # ----------------------    
    print("Cross Validation Results ")
    outcomes = []
    description = []
    shortDescription = []
    for shtDes, des, model in model_List:
        cv_results = cross_val_score(model, X_train, y_train, cv = 10,
                                     scoring='accuracy', n_jobs = -1, verbose = 0)
        outcomes.append(cv_results)
        description.append(des)
        shortDescription.append(shtDes)
        prt_string = "\n %s:\n \tMean Accuracy: %f (Std: %f)" % (des,cv_results.mean()
                                                                    , cv_results.std())
        print(prt_string)

    # ------------------------------------------------------------------
    ## Visualise the outcomes / results from Cross Validation
    # ------------------------------------------------------------------    
    fig = plt.figure()
    fig.suptitle('Cross Validation Results (Algorithm Comparison)')
    plt.ylabel("Accuracy")
    plt.xlabel("Algorithm")
    ax = fig.add_subplot(111)
    plt.boxplot(outcomes)
    ax.set_xticklabels(shortDescription)
    plt.show()

    # ------------------------------------------------------------------    
    ## Training & Fitting of each Algorithm with training Dataset
    # ------------------------------------------------------------------    
    print('\nEvaluate Algorithms (Accuracy, Classification Report, Confusion Matrix) ... ... ... ')
    
    for shtDes, des, model in model_List:   
        
        #model fitting or training
        trained_Model = model.fit(X_train, y_train)
        
        ##Evaluation of trained Algorithm (or Model) and result
        pred_Class          = trained_Model.predict(X_test)
        acc         = accuracy_score(y_test, pred_Class)
        classReport = classification_report(y_test, pred_Class)
        confMatrix  = confusion_matrix(y_test, pred_Class) 

        print("\n%s: " % (des))
        print('The accuracy: {}'.format(acc))
        print('The Classification Report:\n {}'.format(classReport))
        print('The Confusion Matrix:\n {}'.format(confMatrix))
